Steps.Message: Update at 11:39 - We're very sorry we've had to switch off your electricity. Our engineers have turned off the power in the Norwich, NR13 area for safety so they can repair an underground network fault. Our estimated time to have your power back on is between 13:00 and 14:00. If you'd like more information about why we sometimes have to switch power off to work; here's a short video https://bit.ly/3cYez0V. We'll keep you updated with progress.

We became aware of this power cut at 11:21. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
Steps.Name: We are restoring customers automatically
